Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.process

This package contains classes related to process management.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeProcessStateReader Defines interface for reading process state from storage.
IAeProcessStateWriter Defines interface for writing process state to storage.
IAeProcessWrapperMap Defines interface used by persistent process manager to map process ids to process wrappers (which are instances of AeProcessWrapper.
IAeProcessWrapperMapCallback Defines the interface for an instance of IAeProcessWrapperMap to call back to its owner.
 

Class Summary
AeProcessStateReader Reads process state from persistent storage.
AeProcessStateWriter Writes process state to persistent storage.
AeProcessWrapper Wraps a process with its reference count and state.
AeProcessWrapperMap Maps process ids to process wrappers.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.process Description

This package contains classes related to process management.
